{"tid":2492800,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔盈利勝大家樂、大快活　隨時問鼎全港最賺錢餐飲股寶座？","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T12:24:09.000Z","uid":1086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"11bbeaa90e36aadae9f31e8c9cb0717c05ce638b","tid":2492800,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_1024.jpg&h=c0a30737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚仔上市踏出第一步。在香港經營「譚仔雲南米線」及「譚仔三哥米線」品牌的譚仔國際，正式向聯交所遞交上市申請。根據譚仔初步招股書，譚仔本港分店數目雖不及本港快餐龍頭大家樂 （00341） 及大快活 （00052） ，但以最近一個財年計，譚仔盈利最多。若譚仔成功上市，隨時問鼎最賺錢餐飲股寶座。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_GROUPPHOTO5_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_GROUPPHOTO5_1024.jpg&h=48d2a03e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_GROUPPHOTO2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_GROUPPHOTO2_1024.jpg&h=35a1a666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_GROUPPHOTO_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_GROUPPHOTO_1024.jpg&h=2b0fdbe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_GROUPPHOTO3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_GROUPPHOTO3_1024.jpg&h=e8377fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_GROUPPHOTO4_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_GROUPPHOTO4_1024.jpg&h=954479bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港快餐龍頭大家樂旗下擁有多個品牌包括大家樂、上海姥姥、米線陣、意粉屋等，在截至去年3月底止年度，大家樂收入高達近80億元，但由於銷售成本同樣高昂，大家樂上財年僅賺7360萬元。大快活的情況相若，雖然收入逾30億元，但由於毛利率僅得9.2%（與大家樂相同），盈利僅6090萬元。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意，在截至去年3月底止年度，大家樂及大快活的收入分別是譚仔的4.7倍及1.7倍，而且兩者在香港店舖數目皆高於譚仔，但譚仔的盈利卻比兩者高。 根據初步招股書，譚仔於上財年賺1.9億元，分別較大家樂及大快活高1.6倍及2.1倍。另外，譚仔盈利亦高過太興 （06811） 近6成。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意，譚仔的毛利率高達73.2%，是大家樂、大快活、太興、翠華中最高，<span class=\"red\">但各公司對毛利的計算方法不同，有關比率未必可直接比較</span>。<br />\n<br />\n譚仔的毛利率根據總收益減已消耗食物及飲料成本；及中央廚房成本（主要包括員工成本、耗材及包裝、水電 開支、使用權資產折舊、租金及相關開支、租賃負債利息和維修及保養等）計算。反觀，大家樂的毛利，相等於收益減銷售成本，銷售成本包括原材料及包裝成本、折舊及攤銷、租金開支、其他經營開支等，<span class=\"red\">所扣減的成本項目較多，故毛利較低，毛利率也自然較低</span>。"},{"pid":"4749f637ecaee625af230a7d1dca31aa8c129bd1","tid":2492800,"uid":120499,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"11bbeaa90e36aadae9f31e8c9cb0717c05ce638b","tid":2492800,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_1024.jpg&h=c0a30737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚仔上市踏出第一步。在香港經營「譚仔雲南米線」及「譚仔三哥米線」品牌的譚仔國際，正式向聯交所遞交上市申請。根據譚仔初步招股書，譚仔本港分店數目雖不及本港快餐龍頭大家樂 （00341） 及大快活 （00052） ，但以最近一個財年計，譚仔盈利最多。若譚仔成功上市，隨時問鼎最賺錢餐飲股寶座。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2934116/160421_GROUPPHOTO5_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2934116%2F160421_GROUPPHOTO5_1024.jpg&h=48d2a03e&s={SIZ